===Etymology===
From {{F.}} {{term|palais|lang=fr}}, which comes from {{L.}} {{term|palatium|lang=la}}, in reference to the [[Palatine]] Hill, one of the seven hills of Rome, where Rome's aristocracy built large, beautiful residences.

